name: AudioTennis
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: audio tennis
des:
Ben has challenged you to Audio Tennis! Show him what you've got on the court by using the right words to whack the ball back!

You and Ben will face off in epic sets that include three unique rounds, each with their own way to play. For example, in "Alphabet Race," hit the ball back by saying a word that starts with the next letter of the alphabet. The better your vocab skills are, the better you'll play!

 There are tons of cool titles to earn for various achievements. Can you climb the ranks as a Rookie and become an Audio Tennis Legend?
